Welcome to control board operation for Country

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:11.760
Flame products. As we go through the controls,
we ll split the screen to show you the codes

00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:17.410
that are displayed on the back of the control
panel. To start your appliance, make the appropriate

00:00:17.410 --> 00:00:22.720
preparations according to the operations video
tutorial for your Country Flame unit. Once

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:27.550
you ve started the initial fire inside the
firepot, you ll enter into prime mode to establish

00:00:27.550 --> 00:00:34.840
a proper operating flame. To enter prime mode,
push start and hold for 15 seconds. The control

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:40.940
panel illuminates and the code on the back
changes to P. To exit prime mode, push and

00:00:40.940 --> 00:00:51.570
hold the start button for 5 seconds. To begin
the startup sequence, push and hold START

00:00:51.570 --> 00:01:00.100
for 5 seconds. The lightning bolt light will
turn on. The heat sensor will confirm proof

00:01:00.100 --> 00:01:07.689
of fire and the auger will begin to feed fuel
as indicated by the auger light. And the unit

00:01:07.689 --> 00:01:12.149
will automatically enter into a level 3 heat
setting as indicated by the thermometer setting

00:01:12.149 --> 00:01:17.810
here. The unit is now in full operation mode
and you are able to adjust the heat settings

00:01:17.810 --> 00:01:28.319
by pressing the red up or blue down arrows.
Hi-Way Patrol Mode: In the event that one

00:01:28.319 --> 00:01:33.350
of the sensors faults out, the control panel
will flash all of its lights indicating that

00:01:33.350 --> 00:01:39.560
it has entered highway patrol mode. To exit
this mode you will have to reset the control

00:01:39.560 --> 00:01:44.189
board. To do this, press the up arrow, down
arrow and the start button all at the same

00:01:44.189 --> 00:01:56.799
time. The unit has now entered into cool down
mode. Hot Restart: If the unit still has an

00:01:56.799 --> 00:02:01.960
active flame while in its cool down mode and
you wish to restart the appliance, you have

00:02:01.960 --> 00:02:07.229
the option of a hot restart. To enter this
mode, hold down the red up arrow for 15 seconds.

00:02:07.229 --> 00:02:21.440
The unit will again enter into its regular
operation mode. Shut Down Mode: To turn the

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:26.010
unit off, simply press and hold the start
button for 5 seconds. This will begin the

00:02:26.010 --> 00:02:29.970
process of cool down ending with a total powering
down of the control panel. [Content_Types].xml

